SELECT a.MODID, a.MNID, a.UPID,a.MNTYPE, a.PUBNAME, a.DESCRIPTION FROM SYS_MENU (nolock) as a WHERE a.MODID= case ':1' when '00' then a.MODID else ':1' end and (PUBNAME <> '' and PUBNAME is not null) order by a.MODID,a.UPID,MNID asc
